OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be good sunny spells
OL,6,Fbetween patchy amounts of cloud. Most
OL,7,Fplaces will remain dry, but the odd
OL,8,Flight passing shower possible in the
OL,9,Fwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with hazy sunny
OL,12,Fspells, but cloudier around the Moray
OL,13,FFirth. Remaining dry for the rest of
OL,14,Fthe night, the best of the clear
OL,15,Fspells in the west.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA dry and bright morning.
OL,18,FEarly cloud in the east will gradually
OL,19,Fclear, leaving good sunny spells for
OL,20,Fthe rest of the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
